.zig-cache/
zig-out/*
.zed
.DS_STORE
/spec.md
bindings/rust/target/
# Zig source vendored into fig-sys at publish time by `zig build vendor-rust`.
bindings/rust/fig-sys/zig/
# Prebuilt static libraries stamped into the per-target payload crates by
# scripts/build-payload-lib.sh (or CI) before publish — regenerated, never committed.
bindings/rust/fig-sys-*/lib/
.diaryx
# License text and README vendored into each crate at publish time by
# `zig build vendor-rust`; the canonical copies live at the repo root
# (LICENSE-MIT, LICENSE-APACHE, and fig.md → the crate's README.md).
bindings/rust/fig/LICENSE-MIT
bindings/rust/fig/LICENSE-APACHE
bindings/rust/fig/README.md
bindings/rust/fig-sys/LICENSE-MIT
bindings/rust/fig-sys/LICENSE-APACHE
bindings/rust/fig-macros/LICENSE-MIT
bindings/rust/fig-macros/LICENSE-APACHE
src/languages/yaml/spec-1.1-tag-repository.md
src/languages/yaml/spec-1.1.md
*.wasm
src/languages/yaml/spec.md
